                  <div class="field-item even">
                    <p align="center"><span style="color:#f26531; font-weight:bold; font-size:20px;">JOIN OUR TEAM OF TOP THINKERS AND INNOVATORS </span><br />
                      <span style="color:#133d8c; font-weight:bold">An environment where collaboration matters and being connected to <br />
                      our extensive opportunity network can really make a difference in your career </span></p>
                    <h3>WORK LIFE AT VERTEX</h3>
                    <p>At Vertex, we operate under the guiding principle that our people are our assets. We partner with our employees to ensure career success. </p>
                    <h3>OUR CULTURE</h3>
                    <p>At Vertex our culture is client focused and employee centric, committed in providing customer and employee success. </p>
                    <p><span class="orange-n-bold">Customer Focused</span> We will provide superior quality consulting services to our clients. We build client trust by listening to our clients, our quality delivery, and being responsive to their needs. We take pride in being viewed as trusted advisor within our client accounts. The client experience is important to us. </p>
                    <p><span class="orange-n-bold">Employee Centric</span> Our people are our most valuable assets. Attracting and retaining top talent is the cornerstone to our success. We believe that when people can collaborate, exchange information and ideas, they are set up to do their best work and for success.  Ideas are encouraged. Work-life integration matters. The employee experience is important to us. </p>
                    <p><span class="orange-n-bold">Customer and Employee Success</span> We believe when we focus on our clients and employees, we set ourselves up for mutual business and career success. We understand that it takes a team to excel within our organization. Innovation is our obsession. Through our employees we are committed to driving innovation and creating business value. If you are looking for an organization to  where you can connect, collaborate and drive career success; you're at the right place! Join us, and share our passion for innovation and success. </p>
